{
  "stem": "5328.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, when it started already, like, in 1944, the-- the Russians start occupied-- the Russian, like Moscow, Bergen, and going to Kiev and every time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so it used to be in the paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I used to look in the paper, seeing what's going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't think they had any radios.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had a radio, but just in their dining room and their living room-- which I didn't listen to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the newspaper used to come in every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I used to peek in and give a look how-- and see if they are already in Kiev, they're already in Lwow, they are-- you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it-- so this-- this much, I knew what's going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he used-- when he saw me, once, that I am peeking in in the-- in the paper, so he said, you see, we-- you see, we occupied Kiev already.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't worry, he said, we'll get them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll just let them go so far, and then we'll give-- let them go back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we won't give up our-- our territory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And believe-- I make myself that I don't know anything, I don't understand anything, I-- you know, just I-- I'm just--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't supposed to know anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't supposed to know what's going on in the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "German I knew already, that time, how to talk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already-- I-- I taught myself the language.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Supposedly-- I was supposed to be teaching myself being in the house and with the children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I came there, they had a two-year-old baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, later on, they got another baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So with the children, you learn quicker the language than you otherwise do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
